 
# ============================================================================
# Google OAuth Configuration (Optional - for Google login)
# Setup guide: GOOGLE_OAUTH_SETUP.md
# Console: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 
# Required steps:
# 1. Create project di Google Cloud Console
# 2. Enable Google+ API (atau Google Identity Services)
# 3. Configure OAuth consent screen
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 5. Add authorized redirect URIs:
#    - http://localhost:5173/auth/google/callback (dev)
#    - https://yourdomain.pages.dev/auth/google/callback (prod)
# ============================================================================
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret
 
# ============================================================================
# Resend Email Configuration (Optional - for email verification)
# Get from: https://resend.com/api-keys
# 
# NOTE: Domain di Resend biasanya tidak punya inbox.
# Gunakan REPLY_TO_EMAIL untuk menerima balasan user.
# Setup REPLY_TO_EMAIL dengan Gmail/Outlook/Zoho yang punya inbox nyata.
# ============================================================================
RESEND_API_TOKEN=re_your_api_token
FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
REPLY_TO_EMAIL=support@yourdomain.com  # Real inbox (Gmail/Outlook/Zoho)
